project_user_select_policy.name: project_user_select_policy
project_user_select_policy.using:
exists (
            select 1 
            from project_members 
            where project_members.project_id = "projects"."id" 
              and project_members.user_id = (select auth.uid())
          ) or (
            "projects"."creator_id" is not null 
            and "projects"."creator_id" = (select auth.uid())
          )

project_user_update_policy.name: project_user_update_policy
project_user_update_policy.using: exists (select 1 from project_members where project_members.project_id = "projects"."id" and project_members.user_id = (select auth.uid()))

project_user_delete_policy.name: project_user_delete_policy
project_user_delete_policy.using: exists (select 1 from project_members where project_members.project_id = "projects"."id" and project_members.user_id = (select auth.uid()))

chk_tambo_users_legal_consistency.name: chk_tambo_users_legal_consistency
chk_tambo_users_legal_consistency.value: (NOT "tambo_users"."legal_accepted") OR ("tambo_users"."legal_accepted_at" IS NOT NULL AND "tambo_users"."legal_version" IS NOT NULL)
